General Advice.name: No sugar - no sweet in diet. to take rice & potato in less amount. to avoid fasting and meal skipping. to walk 3-4 km  / day. take sugar or glucose if you feel giddy - tremor - perspiration (hypoglycemia). restrict salted and oily (ghee-butter-oil) food beverages - no papad - no pickles.
